      <Value><![CDATA[<p><span class="lead-big"><strong>Jobs, Work Experience and Volunteering</strong></span></p>
<p>In a competitive market place employers are looking for graduates who bring more than just a degree.  During your time at university you are expected to have developed skills such as problem solving, effective communication and leadership. You are also expected to have gained work experience, ideally related to your degree or choice of career.</p>]]></Value>
